= Installation on Ubuntu =

Add a local alias in /etc/hosts 
	127.0.0.1 wouso.local

Install django, mysql, apache and mod-wsgi.

:~# apt-get install libapache2-mod-wsgi python-django apache2 mysql-server python-ldap python-mysqldb

Install pyfacebook and django-facebookconnect:
	git clone git://github.com/ryanmark/django-facebookconnect.git
	git clone git://github.com/sciyoshi/pyfacebook.git
	(python setup.py install)

Edit wouso.local and place it in /etc/apache2/sites-available

:~# a2ensite wouso.local
:~# service apache2 reload

Go to http://wouso.local .
